claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A CONSORT flow diagram showing screening, enrollment, re-enrollment, and randomization of participants across two years (2019–2020) into different influenza vaccine groups (IIV4, ccIIV4, RIV4), exclusions for protocol non-compliance, and final group sizes. does not support the claim because the figure only depicts participant flow and vaccine group assignments without any data on antigenic matching to WHO- or FDA-selected strains. Note: Figure is clear but limited to enrollment and randomization steps; lacks antigenic or strain match information.
